t least 3 years of experience as a Cook Excellent verbal and written communication skills Flexibility to commit to a variable work roster with an availability to work on Saturdays and Sundays Thorough knowledge of measurements, food preparation standards and various cooking techniques Courteous mannerism with a customer focus A team player Cook related job titles: Chef Senior Chef Junior Cook Food Service Worker Culinary Cook Ready to find your next hire? Post a Job Â© 2020 SH Inc. |Â PrivacyÂ |Â TermsÂ |Â Privacy CenterÂ  |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
